{"id":291330,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/04/美国之音-陈光诚侄子狱中患病治疗遭拒-向联合国/","date":"2013-04-30T08:46:09Z","modified":"2013-04-30T08:46:09Z","title":"美国之音 | 陈光诚侄子狱中患病治疗遭拒 向联合国求助","content":"<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://gdb.voanews.com/EECE1A01-E22D-424E-80E2-C77DC0BD7581_w268.jpg\" /><span>陈光诚侄子陈克贵</span></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><span>x</span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://gdb.voanews.com/EECE1A01-E22D-424E-80E2-C77DC0BD7581_mw1024_n_s.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://gdb.voanews.com/EECE1A01-E22D-424E-80E2-C77DC0BD7581_w640_s.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<p><span>陈光诚侄子陈克贵</span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>总部在美国首都华盛顿的人权组织“现在自由”(Freedom Now)星期一向媒体发出英文求援信。信中说，据中国山东临沂监狱狱方透露，流亡美国的中国人权活动人士陈光诚的侄子陈克贵患上急性阑尾炎；但是，狱方不允许他到医院看病，也不允许医生来给他看病。信中说，如果不接受治疗，陈克贵很可能性命难保。</p>\n<p>该组织就陈克贵目前的状况向联合国禁止酷刑与其他反残酷、非人道与压迫人性待遇的特别报告员提交了紧急行动求援信，并呼吁美国政府向中国政府施压，让陈克贵尽快就医。</p></div>\n<p><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://gdb.voanews.com/EECE1A01-E22D-424E-80E2-C77DC0BD7581_w268.jpg\" /><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://gdb.voanews.com/EECE1A01-E22D-424E-80E2-C77DC0BD7581_w640_s.jpg\" /></p>\n<div><img src=\"http://fullrss.net/v/b5751a1dab57f57671c5d503ab58280b/http/www.voachinese.com/content/chen-guangchengs-newphew-has-acute-appendicitics-20130429/1651295.html\" /></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://fullrss.net/\">fullrss.net</a></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://docs.google.com/a/chinadigitaltimes.net/spreadsheet/embeddedform?hl=zh-CN&#038;formkey=dGlaNkplWEluYV9TWUxDQkhfaDlxQmc6MQ\" width=\"510\" height=\"334\" frameborder=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\">Loading&#8230;</iframe></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代 </a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\